cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

This paper deals with the fusion of sensory information from cameras and lidar scans for object recognition and perception in autonomous vehicles. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves robotics and machine learning techniques, which suggest the categories cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for classification and semantic segmentation indicates the category cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves natural language processing techniques for semantic transfer, which suggests the category cs.CL (Computation and Language).
